java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
public class MemberGroupAccountSettings
extends Entity

This is an associative class between MemberGroup and MemberAccountType. It represents those settings for a particular association ofMemberAccountType and MemberGroup, i.e. initial credit, credit limit, etc.
